Final framing
-------------

The project already has:

  - causal anti-leakage law
  - unified graph-node target action
  - post-execution reward
  - Cajtucu paper execution evidence
  - Runtime PPO V0 evidence path
  - Lattice artifact-readiness proof

The missing piece is a reviewed, named learned policy network architecture.

The policy should receive belief, not raw prophecy.
The action should remain a graph-node portfolio.
The distribution must explain its sample.
The reward must come after execution.
The evidence must survive Lattice.
